| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0629 — Recovery Inhibition (siegedsec)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2fbe2c2a-7c99-5287-af6e-6a5e5639eb4c"
